					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Touka is an absolute genius. Once she gets the hang of something, she’s good to go.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"总之桐香是天才，只要抓住诀窍，大部分的事都能马上上手。",
